an><span begin="14.660" end="15.320">誘</span><span begin="15.410" end="15.670">わ</span><span begin="15.690" end="15.900">れ</span><span begin="16.000" end="16.370">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">睡意逐渐袭来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Invited by sleepiness</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nemuke ni sasowarete</span></p><p begin="16.830" end="19.910" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.830" end="17.170">ま</span><span begin="17.210" end="17.520">だ</span><span begin="17.900" end="18.110">点</span><span begin="18.110" end="18.210">い</span><span begin="18.280" end="18.470">て</span><span begin="18.490" end="18.590">る</span><span begin="18.640" end="18.940">蛍</span><span begin="18.990" end="19.230">光</span><span begin="19.330" end="19.910">灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">依然亮着的荧光灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The fluorescent light still turned on</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mada tsuiteru keikoutou</span></p><p begin="20.360" end="22.770" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.360" end="20.400">フ</span><span begin="20.400" end="20.600">ィ</span><span begin="20.620" end="20.720">ル</span><span begin="20.760" end="20.940">ム</span><span begin="20.970" end="21.040">の</span><span begin="21.080" end="21.620">白</span><span begin="21.710" end="22.100">に</span><span begin="22.200" end="22.390">な</span><span begin="22.430" end="22.770">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">化作胶片上的留白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turns into the white of the film</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Firumu no shiro ni naru</span></p><p begin="23.240" end="27.740" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.240" end="24.280">氷</span><span begin="24.350" end="24.480">を</span><span begin="24.540" end="25.020">口</span><span begin="25.030" end="25.290">で</span><span begin="25.390" end="25.770">砕</span><span begin="25.770" end="25.920">い</span><span begin="25.960" end="26.060">て</span><span begin="26.090" end="26.390">キ</span><span begin="26.460" end="26.750">ス</span><span begin="26.800" end="27.080">を</span><span begin="27.140" end="27.390">す</span><span begin="27.430" end="27.740">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在口中咬碎冰块然后亲吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Crushing ice in the mouth and kissing</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koori o kuchi de kudaite kisu o suru</span></p><p begin="28.250" end="31.360" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.250" end="28.640">あ</span><span begin="28.640" end="28.850">あ</span><span begin="29.310" end="29.670">冷</span><span begin="29.710" end="29.910">た</span><span begin="29.910" end="30.060">い</span><span begin="30.080" end="30.400">息</span><span begin="30.420" end="30.690">を</span><span begin="30.740" end="30.940">吐</span><span begin="30.990" end="31.360">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊啊 呼出冰冷的气息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah breathing out a cold breath</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa tsumetai iki o haku</span></p><p begin="31.800" end="35.420" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.800" end="32.160">二</span><span begin="32.170" end="32.370">人</span><span begin="32.390" end="32.490">は</span><span begin="32.560" end="32.750">も</span><span begin="32.750" end="33.050">う</span><span begin="33.110" end="33.800">夢</span><span begin="33.860" end="34.310">の</span><span begin="34.340" end="35.420">中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">两人已然身处梦中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The two of us are already inside a dream</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Futari wa mou yume no naka</span></p><p begin="57.920" end="1:01.110" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.920" end="58.220">冷</span><span begin="58.270" end="58.890">房</span><span begin="58.990" end="59.170">消</span><span begin="59.220" end="59.470">し</span><span begin="59.560" end="59.820">て</span><span begin="59.880" end="1:00.690">君</span><span begin="1:00.740" end="1:01.110">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">关掉冷气 你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turning off the AC you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Reibou keshite kimi wa</span></p><p begin="1:01.690" end="1:06.810" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.690" end="1:02.040">窓</span><span begin="1:02.100" end="1:02.400">辺</span><span begin="1:02.430" end="1:02.720">に</span><span begin="1:02.790" end="1:03.030">も</span><span begin="1:03.120" end="1:03.560">た</span><span begin="1:03.620" end="1:03.970">れ</span><span begin="1:04.640" end="1:05.280">風</span><span begin="1:05.310" end="1:05.570">に</span><span begin="1:05.600" end="1:05.760">揺</span><span begin="1:05.780" end="1:05.940">ら</span><span begin="1:05.980" end="1:06.450">れ</span><span begin="1:06.470" end="1:06.810">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">靠在窗边随风摇曳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Lean by the window swayed by the wind</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Madobe ni motare kaze ni yurareru</span></p><p begin="1:07.160" end="1:09.130" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.160" end="1:07.720">夏</span><span begin="1:07.770" end="1:08.210">の</span><span begin="1:08.250" end="1:09.130">夜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">夏日之夜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Summer night</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Natsu no yoru</span></p><p begin="1:10.220" end="1:14.580" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.220" end="1:10.590">花</span><span begin="1:10.620" end="1:10.750">火</span><span begin="1:10.770" end="1:10.920">は</span><span begin="1:10.960" end="1:11.240">今</span><span begin="1:11.300" end="1:11.810">年</span><span begin="1:11.870" end="1:12.290">も</span><span begin="1:12.430" end="1:12.830">見</span><span begin="1:12.890" end="1:13.210">れ</span><span begin="1:13.260" end="1:13.770">な</span><span begin="1:13.820" end="1:14.220">い</span><span begin="1:14.330" end="1:14.580">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">今年也看不了烟花了呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can&apos;t see the fireworks this year either huh</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hanabi wa kotoshi mo mirenai ne</span></p><p begin="1:15.770" end="1:20.270" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:15.770" end="1:15.940">不</span><span begin="1:15.990" end="1:16.450">満</span><span begin="1:16.480" end="1:16.700">げ</span><span begin="1:16.720" end="1:17.210">に</span><span begin="1:18.620" end="1:19.340">頷</span><span begin="1:19.340" end="1:19.490">い</span><span begin="1:19.540" end="1:19.780">た</span><span begin="1:19.900" end="1:20.270">君</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">面露不满地点了点头的你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You nodded looking dissatisfied</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fumange ni unazuita kimi</span></p><p begin="1:20.750" end="1:23.250" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:20.750" end="1:21.040">重</span><span begin="1:21.110" end="1:21.300">た</span><span begin="1:21.300" end="1:21.450">い</span><span begin="1:21.800" end="1:22.380">瞼</span><span begin="1:22.400" end="1:22.580">を</span><span begin="1:22.770" end="1:23.100">擦</span><span begin="1:23.130" end="1:23.250">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">揉着沉重的眼睑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Rubbing heavy eyelids</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omotai mabuta o kosuru</span></p><p begin="1:23.600" end="1:26.190" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.600" end="1:24.150">煙草</span><span begin="1:24.190" end="1:24.380">の</span><span begin="1:24.680" end="1:25.230">煙</span><span begin="1:25.260" end="1:25.450">が</span><span begin="1:25.590" end="1:25.720">染</span><span begin="1:25.770" end="1:25.960">み</span><span begin="1:25.970" end="1:26.190">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">香烟的烟雾有些刺眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The cigarette smoke stings</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tabako no kemuri ga shimiru</span></p><p begin="1:26.490" end="1:31.780" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.490" end="1:27.030">私</span><span begin="1:27.070" end="1:27.260">の</span><span begin="1:27.540" end="1:28.100">隣</span><span begin="1:28.120" end="1:28.310">で</span><span begin="1:28.440" end="1:28.790">少</span><span begin="1:28.800" end="1:28.890">し</span><span begin="1:28.970" end="1:29.470">窮</span><span begin="1:29.540" end="1:30.000">屈</span><span begin="1:30.050" end="1:30.260">そ</span><span begin="1:30.320" end="1:30.600">う</span><span begin="1:30.660" end="1:30.920">に</span><span begin="1:30.970" end="1:31.490">笑</span><span begin="1:31.500" end="1:31.780">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在我身旁略显局促地笑着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Smiling looking a little cramped next to me</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi no tonari de sukoshi kyuukutsusou ni warau</span></p><p begin="1:32.170" end="1:34.740" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.170" end="1:32.500">甘</span><span begin="1:32.520" end="1:32.730">さ</span><span begin="1:32.780" end="1:32.870">の</span><span begin="1:33.150" end="1:33.450">控</span><span begin="1:33.450" end="1:33.630">え</span><span begin="1:33.650" end="1:33.820">め</span><span begin="1:33.860" end="1:34.050">な</span><span begin="1:34.190" end="1:34.260">ル</span><span begin="1:34.300" end="1:34.550">シ</span><span begin="1:34.550" end="1:34.690">ア</span><span begin="1:34.690" end="1:34.740">ン</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">甜度适中的俄罗斯鸡尾酒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A lightly sweetened Russian</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Amasa no hikaeme na rushian</span></p><p begin="1:34.990" end="1:37.600" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.990" end="1:35.340">静</span><span begin="1:35.390" end="1:35.580">か</span><span begin="1:35.640" end="1:35.810">な</span><span begin="1:36.110" end="1:36.480">温</span><span begin="1:36.480" end="1:36.650">度</span><span begin="1:36.690" end="1:36.860">が</span><span begin="1:37.040" end="1:37.390">包</span><span begin="1:37.430" end="1:37.600">む</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">被静谧的温度包围</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A quiet temperature envelops us</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shizuka na ondo ga tsutsumu</span></p><p begin="1:37.890" end="1:42.200" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:37.890" end="1:38.190">愛</span><span begin="1:38.240" end="1:38.450">し</span><span begin="1:38.450" end="1:38.610">い</span><span begin="1:38.970" end="1:39.350">想</span><span begin="1:39.350" end="1:39.540">い</span><span begin="1:39.560" end="1:39.760">は</span><span begin="1:40.050" end="1:40.310">溶</span><span begin="1:40.400" end="1:41.120">け</span><span begin="1:41.140" end="1:41.810">合</span><span begin="1:41.810" end="1:42.200">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">爱恋的思绪相互交融</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Beloved feelings melt together</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kanashii omoi wa tokeau</span></p><p begin="1:42.520" end="1:47.920" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.520" end="1:43.550">味</span><span begin="1:43.610" end="1:43.900">気</span><span begin="1:44.000" end="1:44.310">な</span><span begin="1:44.310" end="1:44.500">い</span><span begin="1:44.540" end="1:44.850">日</span><span begin="1:44.890" end="1:45.040">々</span><span begin="1:45.070" end="1:45.380">も</span><span begin="1:45.380" end="1:45.760">二</span><span begin="1:45.780" end="1:45.960">人</span><span begin="1:45.980" end="1:46.090">で</span><span begin="1:46.110" end="1:46.440">寄</span><span begin="1:46.460" end="1:46.730">り</span><span begin="1:46.780" end="1:47.180">添</span><span begin="1:47.180" end="1:47.400">え</span><span begin="1:47.460" end="1:47.920">ば</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使是乏味的日子 只要两人相依相偎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even dull days if we stay close together</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ajikenai hibi mo futari de yorisoeba</span></p><p begin="1:48.260" end="1:51.280" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.260" end="1:48.460">き</span><span begin="1:48.460" end="1:48.620">っ</span><span begin="1:48.620" end="1:48.860">と</span><span begin="1:49.280" end="1:49.700">心</span><span begin="1:49.700" end="1:50.040">配</span><span begin="1:50.070" end="1:50.280">は</span><span begin="1:50.280" end="1:50.400">要</span><span begin="1:50.430" end="1:50.730">ら</span><span begin="1:50.760" end="1:50.970">な</span><span begin="1:50.970" end="1:51.280">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一定就无需担心</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Surely there is no need to worry</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kitto shinpai wa iranai</span></p><p begin="1:51.810" end="1:54.210" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.810" end="1:52.040">こ</span><span begin="1:52.070" end="1:52.180">の</span><span begin="1:52.190" end="1:52.370">部</span><span begin="1:52.370" end="1:52.570">屋</span><span begin="1:52.570" end="1:52.720">に</span><span begin="1:52.770" end="1:53.560">帰</span><span begin="1:53.620" end="1:53.810">れ</span><span begin="1:53.880" end="1:54.210">ば</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要回到这个房间</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If we return to this room</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono heya ni kaereba</span></p><p begin="1:54.660" end="2:00.290" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.660" end="1:55.350">堅</span><span begin="1:55.400" end="1:55.880">苦</span><span begin="1:55.940" end="1:56.260">し</span><span begin="1:56.290" end="1:56.450">く</span><span begin="1:56.490" end="1:56.720">て</span><span begin="1:56.860" end="1:57.170">息</span><span begin="1:57.190" end="1:57.340">が</span><span begin="1:57.380" end="1:57.460">詰</span><span begin="1:57.550" end="1:57.880">ま</span><span begin="1:57.920" end="1:58.200">る</span><span begin="1:58.290" end="1:58.640">よ</span><span begin="1:58.640" end="1:58.810">う</span><span begin="1:58.860" end="1:59.340">な</span><span begin="1:59.700" end="2:00.290">街</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">令人感到拘谨而窒息的城市</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The stiff and suffocating city</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Katakurushikute iki ga tsumaru you na machi</span></p><p begin="2:00.730" end="2:02.800" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.730" end="2:01.020">真</span><span begin="2:01.120" end="2:01.480">空</span><span begin="2:01.480" end="2:01.650">の</span><span begin="2:01.700" end="2:02.140">暗</span><span begin="2:02.180" end="2:02.800">闇</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">真空的黑暗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The vacuum of darkness</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinkuu no kurayami</span></p><p begin="2:03.270" end="2:06.850" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.270" end="2:03.620">今</span><span begin="2:03.640" end="2:03.780">は</span><span begin="2:03.800" end="2:04.170">遥</span><span begin="2:04.210" end="2:04.510">か</span><span begin="2:04.580" end="2:04.930">遠</span><span begin="2:05.030" end="2:05.240">く</span><span begin="2:05.300" end="2:05.780">に</span><span begin="2:05.780" end="2:06.090">居</span><span begin="2:06.110" end="2:06.850">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">此刻都在遥远的彼方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Are far away right now</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima wa haruka tooku ni iru</span></p><p begin="2:17.880" end="2:20.230" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.880" end="2:18.470">水</span><span begin="2:18.560" end="2:19.630">中</span><span begin="2:19.670" end="2:20.230">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仿佛在水中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Inside the water</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suichuu ni</span></p><p begin="2:20.720" end="2:23.200" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:20.720" end="2:21.370">沈</span><span begin="2:21.460" end="2:21.680">む</span><span begin="2:21.770" end="2:22.180">よ</span><span begin="2:22.180" end="2:22.510">う</span><span begin="2:22.590" end="2:23.200">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">缓缓下沉般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As if sinking</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shizumu you ni</span></p><p begin="2:23.640" end="2:29.070" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.640" end="2:24.240">輪</span><span begin="2:24.280" end="2:25.360">郭</span><span begin="2:25.460" end="2:25.780">が</span><span begin="2:26.160" end="2:26.780">ぼ</span><span begin="2:26.840" end="2:27.340">や</span><span begin="2:27.500" end="2:27.710">け</span><span begin="2:27.820" end="2:28.070">て</span><span begin="2:28.150" end="2:28.450">消</span><span begin="2:28.450" end="2:28.560">え</span><span begin="2:28.630" end="2:28.820">て</span><span begin="2:28.890" end="2:29.070">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">轮廓变得模糊直至消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The outlines blur and fade away</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Rinkaku ga boyakete kieteku</span></p><p begin="2:29.330" end="2:34.650" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.330" end="2:29.910">歌</span><span begin="2:29.970" end="2:31.130">声</span><span begin="2:31.160" end="2:31.550">は</span><span begin="2:32.210" end="2:32.850">泡</span><span begin="2:32.890" end="2:33.080">に</span><span begin="2:33.160" end="2:33.960">変</span><span begin="2:34.000" end="2:34.330">わ</span><span begin="2:34.370" end="2:34.650">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">歌声化作了泡沫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The singing voice turns into bubbles</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Utagoe wa awa ni kawaru</span></p><p begin="2:35.040" end="2:39.360" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.040" end="2:35.670">月</span><span begin="2:35.700" end="2:35.950">に</span><span begin="2:36.050" end="2:36.810">照</span><span begin="2:36.860" end="2:37.440">ら</span><span begin="2:37.550" end="2:38.200">さ</span><span begin="2:38.290" end="2:38.820">れ</span><span begin="2:38.990" end="2:39.360">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">沐浴在月光之下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Illuminated by the moon</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuki ni terasarete</span></p><p begin="2:41.110" end="2:43.860" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.110" end="2:41.440">少</span><span begin="2:41.480" end="2:41.670">し</span><span begin="2:41.710" end="2:41.770">く</span><span begin="2:41.840" end="2:42.150">す</span><span begin="2:42.200" end="2:42.420">ぐ</span><span begin="2:42.420" end="2:42.560">っ</span><span begin="2:42.560" end="2:42.910">た</span><span begin="2:42.910" end="2:43.100">い</span><span begin="2:43.130" end="2:43.520">よ</span><span begin="2:43.520" end="2:43.620">う</span><span begin="2:43.660" end="2:43.860">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仿佛有些发痒般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Feeling slightly ticklish</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukoshi kusuguttai you na</span></p><p begin="2:43.980" end="2:46.480" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:43.980" end="2:44.300">眠</span><span begin="2:44.330" end="2:44.520">気</span><span begin="2:44.530" end="2:44.610">に</span><span begin="2:44.650" end="2:45.320">誘</span><span begin="2:45.400" end="2:45.710">わ</span><span begin="2:45.710" end="2:45.920">れ</span><span begin="2:46.010" end="2:46.480">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">睡意逐渐袭来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Invited by sleepiness</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nemuke ni sasowarete</span></p><p begin="2:46.840" end="2:49.900" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:46.840" end="2:47.160">ま</span><span begin="2:47.220" end="2:47.430">だ</span><span begin="2:47.890" end="2:48.110">点</span><span begin="2:48.110" end="2:48.220">い</span><span begin="2:48.280" end="2:48.480">て</span><span begin="2:48.490" end="2:48.580">る</span><span begin="2:48.630" end="2:48.920">蛍</span><span begin="2:48.980" end="2:49.240">光</span><span begin="2:49.330" end="2:49.900">灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">依然亮着的荧光灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The fluorescent light still turned on</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mada tsuiteru keikoutou</span></p><p begin="2:50.370" end="2:52.780" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:50.370" end="2:50.420">フ</span><span begin="2:50.420" end="2:50.620">ィ</span><span begin="2:50.630" end="2:50.740">ル</span><span begin="2:50.770" end="2:50.930">ム</span><span begin="2:50.960" end="2:51.060">の</span><span begin="2:51.090" end="2:51.660">白</span><span begin="2:51.730" end="2:52.080">に</span><span begin="2:52.180" end="2:52.380">な</span><span begin="2:52.440" end="2:52.780">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">化作胶片上的留白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turns into the white of the film</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Firumu no shiro ni naru</span></p><p begin="2:53.230" end="2:57.940" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:53.230" end="2:54.260">氷</span><span begin="2:54.310" end="2:54.480">を</span><span begin="2:54.540" end="2:55.030">口</span><span begin="2:55.070" end="2:55.330">で</span><span begin="2:55.410" end="2:55.770">砕</span><span begin="2:55.770" end="2:55.930">い</span><span begin="2:55.960" end="2:56.060">て</span><span begin="2:56.100" end="2:56.390">キ</span><span begin="2:56.450" end="2:56.810">ス</span><span begin="2:56.830" end="2:57.100">を</span><span begin="2:57.160" end="2:57.390">す</span><span begin="2:57.440" end="2:57.940">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在口中咬碎冰块然后亲吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Crushing ice in the mouth and kissing</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koori o kuchi de kudaite kisu o suru</span></p><p begin="2:58.250" end="3:01.360" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:58.250" end="2:58.620">あ</span><span begin="2:58.620" end="2:58.870">あ</span><span begin="2:59.310" end="2:59.650">冷</span><span begin="2:59.700" end="2:59.900">た</span><span begin="2:59.900" end="3:00.050">い</span><span begin="3:00.070" end="3:00.390">息</span><span begin="3:00.410" end="3:00.670">を</span><span begin="3:00.720" end="3:00.960">吐</span><span begin="3:01.020" end="3:01.360">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊啊 呼出冰冷的气息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah breathing out a cold breath</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa tsumetai iki o haku</span></p><p begin="3:01.820" end="3:06.130" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:01.820" end="3:02.190">二</span><span begin="3:02.210" end="3:02.380">人</span><span begin="3:02.410" end="3:02.520">は</span><span begin="3:02.590" end="3:02.780">も</span><span begin="3:02.780" end="3:03.100">う</span><span begin="3:03.160" end="3:03.790">夢</span><span begin="3:03.860" end="3:04.310">の</span><span begin="3:04.350" end="3:06.130">中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">两人已然身处梦中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The two of us are already inside a dream</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Futari wa mou yume no naka</span></p></div></body></tt>